00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:05.599
I was at a kind of crossroads in my life.

00:00:05.599 --> 00:00:09.199
Should I go to Bethel for one month and lose the job?

00:00:09.199 --> 00:00:11.400
We had to make a hard decision.

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:13.800
It was related to neutrality issue.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:18.800
Should I keep my thought after and well-paying job or quit

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:20.800
so that I can focus on my pioneer?

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:23.800
I had to make a decision to go to university

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:26.199
or to serve Jehovah full-time.

00:00:26.199 --> 00:00:30.000
The crossroads really was the attitude toward the decision.

00:00:30.199 --> 00:00:33.600
The foundation of good decision is absolutely

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:35.799
study the Bible and meditation.

00:00:35.799 --> 00:00:37.600
I talked to Jehovah and pray,

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.799
and they will have never done before in my life.

00:00:39.799 --> 00:00:45.600
