00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.399
Think about Jehovah.

00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:58.000
But Jehovah was a student.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.600
When all our daily decisions come together,

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:07.599
we can build a bridge between our life and our long-term spiritual goal.

00:01:07.599 --> 00:01:10.799
Truly speaking, Jehovah's way is happy.

00:01:10.799 --> 00:01:12.799
Whenever I make him happy,

00:01:12.799 --> 00:01:14.000
that makes me happy too.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.400
So if we planted Jehovah,

00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:19.000
